column3: They send someone down here every 10 years or so.
I wonder if I'll see James down here. Been a while since I saw him.
Don't worry you don't have to be alone any more.
I can't remember exactly why I'm here
Is it just me or do all of these walls look the same.
I just wanted to be a time traveller.
Would I be able to tell if I was inside a video game?
Do you think it'd be OK if I just randomly started quoting song lyrics?
